<li id="menu-item-1618" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page current-page-ancestor current-menu-ancestor current-menu-parent current-page-parent current_page_parent current_page_ancestor menu-item-has-children menu-item-1618"><a href="https://medicine.uic.edu/education/international-education/students/">Students</a>
<ul class="sub-menu">
	<li id="menu-item-1617" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-has-children menu-item-1617"><a href="https://medicine.uic.edu/education/international-education/students/international-visiting-students/">International Visiting Students</a>
